<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>893</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>shèng líng a qiú nǐ yáo xǐng 迦南893</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shèng líng a qiú nǐ yáo xǐng wǒ men de jiā zú zhī shù. shèng líng a qiú nǐ yáo xǐng wǒ men de guó jiā zhī lín.
 ràng wǒ men de guó tǔ zhù zài nǐ yīng xǔ zhī de. jié chū jiā měi de pú táo hé fān shí liú.
 a nǐ zhǔn shí huí lái, a nǐ yào shěn pàn quán de.
 yáo xǐng a, yáo xǐng nǐ quán de de ér nǚ. ràng wǒ men jǐn jǐn wéi rào zhe nǐ.</lyrics>
</song>